    "en": {
      "title": "Water Cut for Kotte on Saturday (25)",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The National Water Supply and Drainage Board announced that a 10-Hour water cut will be in effect for many areas in Kotte from Saturday (25) night.",
        "The National Water Supply and Drainage Board says that the water supply to the following areas will be suspended for 10 hours from 10.00 PM tomorrow (25) to 8.00 AM Sunday (26).",
        "The areas that will be affected are: Ethul Kotte, Pita Kotte, Beddagana, Mirihana, Madiwela, Thalapathpitiya, Udahamulla, Embuldeniya, Nugegoda, Pagoda, from Wijerama junction upto 7th Mile Post junction in Highlevel road and all connected by roads, from Nugegoda junction upto Open University in Nawala.",
        "Two men arrested for illegal stockpiling; over 2,000l diesel recovered"
      ],
